{"title":"friend-links","uid":"09d6e417c0c7ccd48cbe7d08ec33c74a","text":"这里会放几个友站的链接（欢迎有blog的同学前来互链 .friends-group .friend-content { display: flex; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; margin: ...","date":"2021-10-02T08:14:28.000Z","updated":"2021-10-02T08:24:54.290Z","comments":true,"path":"api/pages/friend-links/index.json","covers":[],"excerpt":"","content":"<p>这里会放几个友站的链接（欢迎有blog的同学前来互链</p>\n<div id=\"links\">\n <!-- 友情链接css样式 -->\n<style>\n    .friends-group .friend-content {\n  display: flex;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n  justify-content: center;\n  margin: -8px;\n  border-radius: 8px;\n  justify-content: flex-start;\n  align-items: flex-start;\n  line-height: 1.3;\n}\n.friends-group .friend-content .friend-card {\n  display: flex;\n  border-radius: 4px;\n  box-shadow: 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n  padding: 8px 0;\n  margin: 8px;\n  margin-top: calc(2.25 * 16px + 32px);\n  color: rgba(85,85,85,0.65);\n  background: #f6f6f6;\n  justify-content: flex-start;\n  align-content: flex-start;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  width: calc(100% / 4 - 16px);\n}\n@media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {\n  .friends-group .friend-content .friend-card {\n    width: calc(100% / 4 - 16px);\n  }\n}\n@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {\n  .friends-group .friend-content .friend-card {\n    width: calc(100% / 3 - 16px);\n  }\n}\n@media screen and (max-width: 500px) {\n  .friends-group .friend-content .friend-card {\n    width: calc(100% / 2 - 16px);\n  }\n}\n.friends-group .friend-content .friend-card:hover .friend-left .avatar {\n  transform: scale(1.2) rotate(12deg);\n  box-shadow: 0 2px 4px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 8px 16px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n}\n.friends-group .friend-content .friend-card .friend-left {\n  display: flex;\n  align-self: center;\n}\n.friends-group .friend-content .friend-card .friend-left .avatar {\n  width: 64px;\n  height: 64px;\n  transition: all 0.28s ease;\n  -moz-transition: all 0.28s ease;\n  -webkit-transition: all 0.28s ease;\n  -o-transition: all 0.28s ease;\n  box-shadow: 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n  margin: 16px 8px 4px 8px;\n  margin-top: calc(-1.25 * 16px - 32px);\n  border-radius: 100%;\n  border: 2px solid #fff;\n  background: #fff;\n}\n.friends-group .friend-content .friend-card .friend-right {\n  margin: 4px 8px;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n.friends-group .friend-content .friend-card .friend-right p {\n  text-align: center;\n}\n.friends-group .friend-content .friend-card .friend-right .friend-tags-wrapper {\n  transition: all 0.28s ease;\n  -moz-transition: all 0.28s ease;\n  -webkit-transition: all 0.28s ease;\n  -o-transition: all 0.28s ease;\n  margin-left: -2px;\n  word-break: break-all;\n}\n.friends-group .friend-content .friend-card .friend-right p {\n  margin: 0;\n}\n.friends-group .friend-content .friend-card .friend-right p.friend-name {\n  font-size: 0.8125rem;\n  padding-top: 4px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n}\n.friends-group .friend-content .friend-card .friend-right p.tags {\n  font-size: 0.75rem;\n  display: inline;\n  background: 0 0;\n  overflow-wrap: break-word;\n  padding-right: 4px;\n}\n</style>\n    <div class=\"friends-group\">\n        <h3 class=\"friend-header\">\n            <i class=\"fas fa-user-tie fa-fw\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n            友情链接\n        </h3>\n        <div class=\"friend-content\">\n            \n            <!-- 友情链接卡片 -->\n                <a class=\"friend-card\" style=\"background:#0e83cd; color:#fff\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.meerost.com\">\n                    <div class=\"friend-left\">\n                        <img class=\"avatar\" src=\"https://gitee.com/MeerOst/MeerOstDrawingBed/raw/master/admin/Raumzeit.png\" data-original=\"https://gitee.com/MeerOst/MeerOstDrawingBed/raw/master/admin/Raumzeit.png\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"friend-right\">\n                        <p class=\"friend-name\">MeerOst导航</p>\n                        <div class=\"friend-tags-wrapper\">\n                            <p class=\"tags\">关于MeerOst的,都在这里</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </a>\n            \n            <!-- 友情链接卡片 -->\n                <a class=\"friend-card\" style=\"background:#0e83cd; color:#fff\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://zhiming-xu.github.io\">\n                    <div class=\"friend-left\">\n                        <img class=\"avatar\" src=\"https://tse1-mm.cn.bing.net/th/id/R-C.7a864f07681f187fb572468bfc949977?rik=EyUQGBjtSbMjVw&riu=http%3a%2f%2fpngimg.com%2fuploads%2fgithub%2fgithub_PNG80.png&ehk=sCQlSHnb7Wc8WNPgOilokXbf8jL4g20yv7QFEFpl6ko%3d&risl=&pid=ImgRaw&r=0\" data-original=\"https://tse1-mm.cn.bing.net/th/id/R-C.7a864f07681f187fb572468bfc949977?rik=EyUQGBjtSbMjVw&riu=http%3a%2f%2fpngimg.com%2fuploads%2fgithub%2fgithub_PNG80.png&ehk=sCQlSHnb7Wc8WNPgOilokXbf8jL4g20yv7QFEFpl6ko%3d&risl=&pid=ImgRaw&r=0\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"friend-right\">\n                        <p class=\"friend-name\">Zhiming Xu|Homepage</p>\n                        <div class=\"friend-tags-wrapper\">\n                            <p class=\"tags\">一个厉害的学长的主页</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </a>\n            \n        </div>\n    </div>          \n</div>\n","count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.3k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#links\"><span class=\"toc-text\">\n            \n            友情链接\n        </span></a></li></ol>"}